# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Files that SHOULD be committed (not ignored)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# README.md          — public-facing docs
# CLAUDE.md          — project context for AI agents (useful for contributors)
# LOCAL_DEV.md       — developer setup guide
# IDEA.md            — product concept (inspiration, not competitive intel)
# VISION.md          — public product vision
# Cargo.toml         — dependency manifest
# Cargo.lock         — reproducible builds
# src/               — all source code
# templates/         — all HTML templates
# .cursor/rules/     — mcpolly.mdc (the auto-integration feature)
